item.title: About
item.description: My name is Lucas Li, but you may know me by my online name, Gelzone Unsas. I am a multi-faceted individual with a passion for programming, music production, and game development. As a programmer, I am constantly seeking new ways to improve my skills and knowledge. I am particularly interested in game development and the endless possibilities it offers. My undergraduate studies and senior project in Computer Science have provided me with a strong foundation in programming and software development.
